ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Soft-Play.-Credit-Thomas-Davis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Soft-Play.-Credit-Thomas-Davis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Soft-Play.-Credit-Thomas-Davis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Soft-Play.-Credit-Thomas-Davis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Soft-Play">Soft Play</a> – FKA <a href="/artists/Slaves">Slaves</a> – 分享了他们残酷的新单曲“Act Violently”，并宣布了新专辑“Heavy Jelly”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-on-their-name-change-and-new-music-we-can-be-aggressive-but-we-can-also-have-a-little-cuddle-3603130">软玩他们的更名和新音乐：“我们可以咄咄逼人，但我们也可以拥抱一下”</a></strong></li></ul><p>新曲目延续了之前发行的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-fka-slaves-share-new-single-punks-dead-and-announce-surprise-reading-leeds-sets-3486125">Punk&#39;s Dead</a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-hit-the-gym-for-heavy-new-single-mirror-muscles-3599751">Mirror Muscles</a> 》，并从新金属中汲取了紧张的沉重感和干净的制作风格。它还包含英国朋克元素。</p><p>据一份新闻稿称，这首歌的灵感来自于艾萨克·霍尔曼 (Isaac Holman) 和劳里·文森特 (Laurie Vincent) 在马盖特<a href="/artists/The-Libertines">The Libertines</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-hotel-albion-rooms-margate-carl-barat-video-tour-interview-2770049">Albion Rooms</a>工作室录制专辑时差点被电动滑板车撞到。</p><p> “在返回工作室的整个过程中，我们都在讨论对电动滑板车司机的蔑视。它们应该是非法的，”文森特分享道。 “他们不应该在路上。他们应该需要理论测试。这只是一口值得讨论的丰富的井，而这首歌就是关于这一点的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SOFT PLAY - 暴力行为（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H0WqeDa5ihE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Act Violently》的音乐视频将歌曲的叙事形象化，霍尔曼无论走到哪里都被同一辆电动滑板车困扰：首先在他离开商店时差点溅到他，然后在公园里把他的手机从手中撞落，然后又靠近了在斑马线上撞倒他他最终发誓要以义务警员的方式进行复仇。</p><p> Soft Play 将于 7 月 19 日发行他们的第四张录音室专辑《Heavy Jelly》。这标志着他们以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slaves-announce-return-music-change-name-soft-play-3364247">新乐队名称</a>发行的第一张 LP，也是六年多来的第一个长篇项目。</p><p>专辑的实体格式包括 CD、黑色黑胶唱片、HMV 独家签名 CD 以及仅通过乐队官方商店和精选独立零售商出售的限量绿色黑胶唱片。您可以<a href="https://store.softplayband.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存专辑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752913" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752913" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752913" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="SoftPlay &#39;Heavy Jelly&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752913" class="wp-caption-text"> Soft Play &#39;Heavy Jelly&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>Soft Play &#39;Heavy Jelly&#39; 曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>&#39;万物&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>《朋克已死》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;逞凶&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“艾萨克正在打字……”</strong><br /> <strong>“宾果汁灾难”</strong><br /> <strong>《停机坪上的蠕虫》</strong><br /> <strong>《约翰威克》</strong><br /> <strong>“镜子肌肉”</strong><br /> <strong>“工作头衔”</strong><br /> <strong>《蘑菇和天鹅》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;一切又一无所有&#39;</strong></p><p>乐队表示，这张专辑是以柔术教练的名字命名的，他告诉文森特要表现得像“沉重的果冻”，解释在演示中要给予多大的阻力。这句话最终反映了两人的世界观“生活是沉重的，但也很有趣，”霍尔曼说。</p><p>文森特补充道：“我们不会成为真正雄辩地领导抗议游行的乐队，但我们可能会成为激励你去健身房或开始做一些富有成效的事情的乐队，这也很重要，”他继续说道，“我们能做的就是唱一些相关的事情并与人们分享。”</p><p>霍尔曼继续说道：“不要试图和其他人一样。做你想做的事并享受乐趣。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4scCNBtud6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530